caption: Some cricket and then some beer..
Very beautiful park with many peacocks and beautiful lawn areas. Ideal for spending a lovely afternoon when the weather is nice.

Staff at the entrance very unpleasant and thinking they were superior people, not even a hello, but on the other hand to kick us out because we had 2 children's scooters (2 and 3 years old) no worries! On the other hand, tricycles, strollers and walking sticks are accepted!!! Find the error?! There are play areas inside but children are not welcome, we won't be back!!!!!! What a shame!
November 11 stroll under the sun. A very good moment shared. The rose garden should be even more beautiful when it is in bloom.
